room_title: Escape room "The Speakeasy" by Locked Up - Mishawaka in South Bend
review: Speakeasy was fantastic, came close to finishing but sadly failed. Designed fantastically as riddles were very clever and adequately difficult. 100% recommend.

room_title: Escape room "The Speakeasy" by Locked Up - Mishawaka in South Bend
review: Was so much fun. We didn’t finish the Speakeasy, unfortunately, the time ran out, but I’d definitely do it again.

room_title: Escape room "The Speakeasy" by Locked Up - Mishawaka in South Bend
review: We did the Speakeasy room. Didn't escape but LOVED the experience. Will definitely be returning to try another room.
